                <div class="body">


                    <div class="row clearfix">

                        <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
                            <ol>
                                <li>Our provided Permanent Account Number or PAN,  </li>
                                <li>Our provided Permanent Account Number or PAN, is a means of identifying various taxpayers in the country. PAN is a unique identification number assigned to Indians,</li>
                                <li>system that assigns unique identification number to every Indian tax paying entity. Through this method,</li>
                                <li>This is so majorly because PAN is unaffected by any change of address of the PAN cardholder.</li>
                                <li>Through this method, all tax related information for a person is recorded against a single PAN number which acts as the primary </li>
                                <li>permanent and temporary both. Although, the primary aim for SSN creation was to track individuals for social security purposes</li>



                            </ol>
                        </div>
                    </div>


                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

